This paper deals with the training of neural networks, which is a topic that falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the difficulty of different learning problems, which is relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The concept of intrinsic dimension is a mathematical concept that is commonly used in the field of neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also discusses the classification of images (CIFAR-10) and playing Atari games, which are topics related to computer vision (cs.CV) and control systems (cs.SY), respectively.
